VoikkoSpellService - Spell-checking service for Mac OS X
========================================================

VoikkoSpellService is an open source spell-checking service for Mac OS X.

VoikkoSpellService utilises the Voikko project's libvoikko and suomi-malaga libraries for spell- and grammar checking. Those are included in the binary package.

Supported Mac OS X versions:
============================
- Mac OS X 10.5 (Leopard)
- Mac OS X 10.6 (Snow Leopard)
- Mac OS X 10.7 (Lion)

The component includes binary for both 32-bit and 64-bit targets. 

Voikko projects homepage is at: http://voikko.sourceforge.net/

Installation:
=============
1. Remove old installation of VoikkoSpellService or Soikko and then log out and in.
2. Copy the VoikkoSpellService.app to Library/Services which can be found under your user's home directory. If there is no such directory then create it.
2.1 Alternatively you can enable the spell-checking for every user by copying it under System's Library/Services.
3. Log out and in.

